<%- layout(`Boilerplate/boilerplate`) %>

<link
  rel="stylesheet"
  href="/Stylesheets/REFUND POLICY/refund-policy-styles.css"
/>

<%- include('../../Solutions-Card/solutionsCard.ejs') %>

<div class="refund-policy-container">
  <div class="main-heading">
    <h1>REFUND POLICY</h1>
  </div>

  <p>
    At Digital Benders, we are deeply committed to delivering products and
    services that meet the highest standards of quality, reliability, and
    customer satisfaction. We believe in building long-term relationships with
    our clients by standing behind everything we offer. However, we also
    understand that there may be circumstances where our services or products
    may not fully meet your expectations. In such cases, we want to assure you
    that your concerns will be treated with utmost importance. That’s why we
    have established a transparent, fair, and customer-oriented refund
    policy—one that is designed to protect your rights, ensure accountability on
    our part, and provide you with complete peace of mind throughout your
    experience with us.
  </p>

  <h2 class="secondary-heading">Eligibility for Refund</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>
      Refund requests must be submitted within
      <strong>30 calendar days</strong> from the original purchase date.
    </li>
    <li>
      The product or service in question must be in its
      <strong>original, unused condition</strong> (if applicable).
    </li>
    <li>
      Proof of purchase, such as an invoice or transaction ID, must be provided
      at the time of the request.
    </li>
    <li>
      Certain categories, such as downloadable digital products, custom
      services, or promotional offers, may be <strong>non-refundable</strong>.
      This will be clearly stated at the time of purchase.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="secondary-heading">Processing of Refunds</h2>

  <p>
    Once your refund request has been reviewed and approved by our team, the
    refund process will be initiated promptly. Refunds are typically processed
    within <strong>14 to 22 business days</strong>, depending on your financial
    institution’s processing speed. All refunds will be issued using the
    original method of payment unless otherwise agreed upon in writing.
  </p>

  <p class="note">
    <span>Note:</span> Haris Bhai Project reserves the right to update, modify,
    or revise this refund policy at any time without prior notice. However, any
    changes will be made in accordance with our commitment to transparency and
    fairness. In the rare event of project delays or failure to meet performance
    expectations, customers may be eligible for a
    <strong>full 100% refund</strong> upon case verification by our internal
    Quality Assurance team.
  </p>

  <p>
    We are committed to ensuring your satisfaction and maintaining your trust.
    If you have any questions or concerns regarding our refund process, please
    don’t hesitate to reach out to our support team for immediate assistance.
  </p>
</div>
